NAME Phish Redirect
DESCRIPTION Opens a phishing URL in the target's browser
CATEGORY exploit
PLATFORMS WIN,MAC,LINUX
OPTION URL https://example.com "Phishing page URL"
PLATFORM ALL
DELAY 500
LED_COLOR RED
PRINT Opening phishing URL...
BROWSE_URL {{URL}}
DELAY 3000
MINIMIZE_ALL
LED_COLOR GREEN
PRINT Payload delivered
